5704610&amp;_rdr</a><br />\n<br />\n777已讀不回的六月<br />\n<a href=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/WrBRDev.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWrBRDev.jpg&d=IJ4Nzxd4hLWYFZk0XL5PgX8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=3b6c31a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/WrBRDev.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"2613ddd33d56280fe9c8be053a7fb08f682b10f8","tid":1271681,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:33:54.000Z","msg":"佔領立法會 林鄭都依然冷漠拒絕對話 係唔係想攪到流血收場 為什麼不出來對話 不解決問題<br />\n這是文明社會"},{"pid":"180fd1f0ffa323a148ccd8c82fb1b610bce9dbc4","tid":1271681,"uid":265434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:33:55.000Z","msg":"已經踏入七月，血色的六月看看我們經歷了甚麼？<br />\n一直以爲每一次增加人數能向政府表達我們的訴求，可是事實卻是相反的。103萬人，200萬01人，沒有換來一句表示。只有612的所謂「暴動」(ps.一半還是有政府參與的中信事件演變而成。），造就得利一個暫緩修例。<br />\n200萬01人之後，我們再沒有得到甚麼。<br />\n這樣子，香港的六月過去了。<br />\n昨天，是71遊行，預期了沒有回應的林鄭政府在早上還有一個酒會，舉著杯，喝著酒，無視在外只隔一街的示威者訴求，笑著拍照。<br />\n這是甚麼世界？<br />\n如果我們不再做點甚麼的話，也許這71過後只餘下空蕩的街頭，被那些高官都遺忘了吧..."},{"pid":"86b74e2966a26827c152b91e4985afb99b576324","tid":1271681,"uid":265434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QEowDk6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQEowDk6.png&h=b59fe2c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6215db0095ca3271da9a53a8722c27da9efd1130","tid":1271681,"uid":77030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:35:37.000Z","msg":"文宣出動"},{"pid":"10a7bf32c1b78e9a33c135146df45ab38f289d28","tid":1271681,"uid":265434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:49:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HaMx7iQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHaMx7iQ.png&h=80e80e94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據實時報導，D狗向5分鐘內向龍和道彈左七個催淚彈"},{"pid":"7fbc47e8862c41ee8601b4def3d9b88159190580","tid":1271681,"uid":