。近年還有無準則dq選票，褫奪參選資格。<br />\n<br />\n在香港，在任何一刻，佔領立法會，都是有百份百的正當性，甚至是最有正當性的佔領，沒有之一。<br />\n<br />\n只是要奪回一個本應是屬於人民的地方。<br />\n<br />\n很抱歉，習慣躺著被強暴的人，沒資格指責挺起胸膛的人。<br />\n<br />\n絕對沒資格。"},{"pid":"156879ee3860441714e305e94b0815914f7a1da6","tid":1271681,"uid":265434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tdjDiwb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtdjDiwb.png&h=9aa0f834&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59afb1dfe9e6308ce70f82f88c2ce7e42182be24","tid":1271681,"uid":265434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:05:42.000Z","msg":"姬<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/01yMspM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F01yMspM.png&h=a2600927&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oxcmgh6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOxcmgh6.png&h=8c5753a0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4V7QT4N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4V7QT4N.png&h=15822599&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O9CJuC8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO9CJuC8.png&h=6daf05bb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O4mm0KP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO4mm0KP.png&h=b4612285&s={SIZE}\" />姬<br />\n<br />\n有人整理左"},{"pid":"dc06bf384d9653a988c08548f5eb30bc33c7eaee","tid":1271681,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:06:41.000Z","msg":"狗仔濫權 交通大阻塞<br />\n煲大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98d15bcd36dd9a22e082c5f24b7cf927e04802d","tid":1271681,"uid":137833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:30:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9257e5a8121d74e4155baf20eec0f3c3818744c5","tid":1