集中屌林鄭<br />\n和平示威又唔回應 衝擊又唔回應"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:32:51.000Z","msg":"咁應該重點話做到咁林鄭都拒絕溝通？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:36:22.000Z","msg":"我諗係<br />\n電視都影哂點衝擊<br />\n點兜都兜唔到<br />\n應該將衝突正當化<br />\n可能同台灣大陽花比較<br />\n講下當局從處理手法有咩唔同？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:28:51.000Z","msg":"見立場新聞有篇文係話<br />\n林鄭、文革式藍絲同動用江湖人士嘅人係今次嘅罪魁<br />\n可能可以帶埋尋日暴力事件嘅影響之類？"},{"pid":"05508f42dc37fb197372e75c534e57f2fbb7f732","tid":1271681,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:35:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">立場妹妹英文字幕</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://sendvid.com/iwiag6no\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fiwiag6no&d=IJ4Nzxd4hLWYFZk0XL5PgX8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=fc507e0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sendvid.com/iwiag6no</a>"},{"pid":"db138df965fab6a080fbd5ef5c016e32e30c26c1","tid":1271681,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:36:10.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"1479775fcfa141adef064d08b1cfabd2cf6522b3","tid":1271681,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:52:43.000Z","msg":"【重要文本】<br />\n<strong>《2019.71 香港人宣言》（立會現場宣讀版）</strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GpKcnMT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGpKcnMT.png&h=0ffb531b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ipAyRFe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FipAyRFe.png&h=1697a5e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JPg2K0f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJPg2K0f.png&h=c004443e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《2019.71 香港人宣言》（定稿版）</strong><br />\n<br />\n各位香港市民，<br />\n<br />\n我們是一群來自民間的示威者。萬不得已，我們並不想走上以身對抗暴政的路，以佔領香港特區政府立法會作為我們談判的籌碼；但滿口謊言、滿口歪理的政府卻無意回應香港人不斷走上街的訴求。我們只好以公義、良知、以及對香港、對香港人無窮無盡的愛，去抗衡橫蠻的政府。<br />\n<br />\n香港特區政府成立至今22年，政經民生每況愈下。現任特首林鄭月娥上台後，情況變本加厲，更漠視民間逾百萬民意，推出「送中惡法」。市民於6月起前仆後繼，各盡其力，或和平、或理性、或奮勇、或受傷流血，以一顆熱愛香港之心，懇求政府撤回修例，而政府置若罔聞，不諳民情，竟置香港大眾於不顧，甚至以民為敵。<br />\n<br />\n現任特區政府已非以港人行先，為使政府聆聽港人聲音，我等市民不得不進行各種佔領，不合作運動、乃至今日佔領立法會行動。社會或對我等佔領者有所批評，但追本溯源，社會撕裂之誘因為何？民怨每日俱增之本源為何？香港何辜？香港人何以被追逼至此？我等港人沒有武裝，沒有暴力，只能以秉持正義於心，無畏無懼，奮勇向前。希望能香港政府能及時回首，重回正軌：<br />\n<br />\n我們佔領者，要求政府完成五大訴求：<br />\n<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n「反送中運動」發展至今，在三位年輕市民殉道。我等未忘憂憤，然心存善念，不願香港再有為民主、為自由、為公義再添亡魂。希望社會大眾團結一致，對抗惡法，對抗暴政，共同守護香港。"},{"pid":"f709d6886d4c1a196b7559990e1fbb953f86b3c4","tid":1271681,"uid":52609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:53:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Owq3wd7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOwq3wd7.jpg&h=116179a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n驚大家無散紙搭車"},{"pid":"e2ef91a94218cd2a52508ed8d68918f96c6ce03b","tid":1271681,"uid":265434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:35:15.000Z","msg":"英文版<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YGMqLNZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYGMqLNZ.gif&h=b29f7d26&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E2Gm3zE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE2Gm3zE.png&h=d2934487&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ujOQcs0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FujOQcs0.png&h=ffb7e4ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2vqyUGk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2vqyUGk.png&h=2a45a144&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pdZ4gUF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpdZ4gUF.png&h=a6f5e5e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a24c432d0a45fab0cf16ce28ccd7e8d4ded9c103","tid":1271681,"uid":261433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:37:07.000Z","msg":"咁咪即係hea做囉 同擅離警崗如岀一撤"},{"pid":"e2b82f139b2222520279741d3f7c3ea8b5733ef7","tid":1271681,"uid":65888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:43:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6127305c1bc9b600c74b164c9d4dc8c0bee0dbb8","tid":1271681,"uid":258302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:43:01.000Z","msg":"我明加字幕應該好易<br />\n但我真係唔識<br />\n整咗成晚都不斷死機 <br />\n<br />\n以下係呢條片0032到0410的字幕中英文<br />\n#齊上齊落<br />\n#一齊走<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VvmYfZwO0R4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVvmYfZwO0R4&d=IJ4Nzxd4hLWYFZk0XL5PgX8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=e9ad967f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VvmYfZwO0R4</a><br />\n希望有人見到有用<br />\n<br />\nClose to midnight, 1 July 2019<br />\nLegislative Council of Hong Kong <br />\n七月一日<br />\n香港立法會議事廳<br />\n<br />\n00:32<br />\n<br />\n一齊走<br />\nLeave together<br />\n快啲呀<br />\nQuick<br />\n一齊走<br />\nLeave together<br />\n攻咗入嚟㗎啦留喺度冇意思㗎喇，一齊走啦<br />\nThey (the police) are coming in. There's no use staying, let&rsquo;s leave<br />\n唔可以為港共政權犧牲㗎<br />\nDon't waste your life for this HK-Communist regime<br />\n啱啱入嚟嘅朋友⋯示威者大概有一百人左右，佢哋直接行去拒絕離開嘅示威者嗰度<br />\nWhat we are seeing now is about 100 protesters streaming toward the protesters who refuse to retreat<br />\n走<br />\nGo<br />\n走<br />\nGo<br />\n小心小心<br />\nWatch out watch out<br />\n一齊走啦<br />\nLeave together<br />\n慢慢走<br />\nSlowly<br />\n[掌聲]<br />\n[Applause]<br />\n走，走<br />\nGo，go<br />\n讓呀讓呀<br />\nMake way<br />\n走呀走呀全部一定要走呀<br />\nGo, go , all must go<br />\n冷靜冷靜<br />\nClam, clam<br />\n唔好推唔好推<br />\nDon&rsquo;t push<br />\n一齊走一齊走一齊走一齊走<br />\nLeave together, leave together, leave together<br />\n<br />\n0211<br />\n一齊走呀<br />\nLeave together<br />\n齊上齊落呀<br />\nWe charge and withdraw together<br />\n[記者交談 Reporter speaking]<br />\n<br />\n啱啱有一群示威者喺立法會煲底上咗嚟<br />\nJust now a group of protesters burst in from the outside the Legco Building<br />\n人數大概有一百人 <br />\nThere are around 100 of them<br />\n我哋訪問其中一位示威者<br />\nI&rsquo;ll speak to one of them<br />\n點解會有呢個行動上嚟<br />\nWhy are you here<br />\n因為我哋透過Telegram知道有4個義士會留低<br />\nWe saw it on Telegram that there are 4 people staying<br />\n所以我哋決定全部人一齊上嚟抬佢哋一齊走<br />\nSo all of us have decided to come here to pull them out<br />\n佢哋唔走我哋都唔走<br />\nIf they don&rsquo;t go, we won&rsquo;t either<br />\n我哋拱佢哋一齊走<br />\n<br />\n而家都好接近12點嘅死線，你哋驚唔驚入到嚟會出唔番去<br />\nWe are now very close to the midnight deadline. Are you scared that you won&rsquo;t be able to leave this building now you are in<br />\n個個都好驚，但仲驚聽日見唔到佢哋4個<br />\nEveryone of us are very scared but worse is the possibility of not being able to see the 4 of them again tomorrow<br />\n所以我哋先一齊入嚟一齊走<br />\nThat&rsquo;s why we are in here and we will leave together<br />\n有冇人出嚟號召定係煲底自發有呢個行動<br />\nIs this a call from the people inside the Legco? Or initiated by those who stayed outside?<br />\n本身揸住大聲公嘅就唔想，就話尊重死士嘅決定<br />\nThe mic-man said no; he said he would respect the &ldquo;martyrs&rsquo;&rdquo; wishes<br />\n但係⋯一齊上去，叫佢哋一齊走<br />\nBut we decided to go up together<br />\n係所有人一齊決定嘅<br />\nSo this was a consensus from us all<br />\n<br />\n記者由立法會議事廳行番呢條電梯落咗立法會地下<br />\nNow I have just walked form the Council Chamber to the ground floor<br />\n啱啱聽到訪問喺立法會煲底⋯<br />\nAs you have heard&hellip;<br />\n⋯靠近立法會所謂12點嘅死線<br />\n&hellip;As the time draws near to the midnight deadline<br />\n其實所有上嚟嘅示威者都非常之驚<br />\nIn fact all of them are very scared <br />\n但佢哋好驚聽日朝早起見唔番<br />\nBut their worse fear was never being able too see them again&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n04:10 finish"},{"pid":"335327647a42b94a094eacca645cc468174faf85","tid":1271681,"uid":188969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:44:34.000Z","msg":"文宣既戰爭開始！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1278390\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1278390</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">簡單文宣<br />\nSave低喜歡既圖，不停send俾人<br />\nShare 此link plzz </span></span>"},{"pid":"64e190876b534f40743afa9deec6396a0700c7ac","tid":1271681,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:22:14.000Z","msg":"［文宣戰對準台灣］蔡英文要做多d助攻<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1282101\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1282101</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c97dacea5a8cf7d2910ada39b9a7d3401059ac15","tid":1271681,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c441db8ec7f0a1099fadd82446896857842bc3a","tid":1271681,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e25eb3d8b0f4a8c6bd58aead6a8c354c7decff4","tid":1271681,"uid":262618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:25:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9970085e68ea8944dbba1ab46f2c9a9a71af90de","tid":1271681,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b43ed47ea307effb8c85b0bebf9589e4a3b2d969","tid":1271681,"uid":167277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:42:05.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"d50f7ec1735d7992d2f657efffdf02a2c18695e8","tid":1271681,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:44:04.000Z","msg":"我無野講<br />\n我要見律師<br />\n我要飲水<br />\n我要食飯"},{"pid":"7c2657a6c1d36128f782707b969425d9cbb313e4","tid":1271681,"uid":38526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:47:58.000Z","msg":"對外文宣應唔應該整埋630班狗選擇性執法,甚至原告變被告<br />\n我冇野講 6549 9452"},{"pid":"4e4c3a8592f3213f2c1e4618f26a74105ed3d590","tid":1271681,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T00:55:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}